{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the World of Drakefall in this roguelike deckbuilder. Build your deck, discover powerful items, and journey through swamps and mountain peaks with a familiar playstyle. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tell us what do you think about Drakefall</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/join-us-on-discord.gif?t=1733754061\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evolving Deck Construction</strong>: Make strategic card choices! Explore and acquire hundreds of cards to build your deck with every attempt to conquer the ruptured world of Drakefall. Pick cards that synergize well to effectively defeat foes and challenge theruling dragons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/all-cards.gif?t=1733754061\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Dynamic World</strong>: Each journey through the fractured realm of Drakefall is unique. Opt for perilous or secure paths, encounter diverse enemies, select varied cards, uncover distinct relics, and face different challanges every time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143810/extras/drakefall-map-gif.gif?t=1733754061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Harness the Power of the Stars:</strong> Engage in the mystical art of <strong>Starbinding</strong>, where you channel the celestial energies to gain powerful bonuses. As you ascend the floors, the potency of these bonuses increases, offering strategic advantages. Choose the right moment to claim your active bonus and shape your journey through the world of Drakefall.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><br><img cla